      • getDummyRDotJavaPath

        Optional<Path> getDummyRDotJavaPath(TargetNode<?,?> targetNode)
        Parameters:
        targetNode - node to generate the path to
        Returns:
        the project-relative path to a directory structure under which the R.class file can be found (the structure will be the same as the package path of the R class). A path should be returned only if the given TargetNode requires the R.class to compile.
